[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, manje od 1% zgrada

1857
01:27:45,479 --> 01:27:45,779
[SPEAKER_01] ima projekt.

1858
01:27:45,779 --> 01:27:46,739
[SPEAKER_01] Kako im iste obnoviti zgrade?

1859
01:27:49,060 --> 01:27:50,579
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, morate projekte napraviti.

1860
01:27:50,579 --> 01:27:51,579
[SPEAKER_01] Di su projekte?

1861
01:27:51,579 --> 01:27:52,779
[SPEAKER_01] Čak i ako imamo novac

1862
01:27:52,779 --> 01:27:54,180
[SPEAKER_01] nemate projekata.

1863
01:27:54,180 --> 01:27:55,420
[SPEAKER_01] Nemerite napraviti natječaj

1864
01:27:55,420 --> 01:27:55,979
[SPEAKER_01] za obnovu

1865
01:27:55,979 --> 01:27:56,760
[SPEAKER_01] kad nemate projekte.

1866
01:27:56,760 --> 01:27:59,119
[SPEAKER_01] Svi ljudi bi šutili

1867
01:27:59,119 --> 01:28:00,640
