1884
01:28:20,619 --> 01:28:21,920
[SPEAKER_01] Prije ti primjerice,

1885
01:28:21,920 --> 01:28:22,680
[SPEAKER_01] ja mislim da će milijarda

1886
01:28:22,680 --> 01:28:23,899
[SPEAKER_01] otići na obnovu katedrale.

1887
01:28:23,899 --> 01:28:25,199
