1896
01:28:33,640 --> 01:28:34,159
[SPEAKER_01] Daj da vidim.

1897
01:28:34,159 --> 01:28:35,479
[SPEAKER_01] U kako je to danas stanje?

1898
01:28:35,479 --> 01:28:36,699
[SPEAKER_01] Nikakom.

1899
