1905
01:28:45,699 --> 01:28:47,039
[SPEAKER_01] recimo obnoviti privatne zgrade.

1906
01:28:47,039 --> 01:28:48,619
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, tužno i jadno.

1907
01:28:48,619 --> 01:28:49,739
[SPEAKER_01] Pitanje je koliko će ovi ljudi

1908
01:28:49,739 --> 01:28:50,579
[SPEAKER_01] biti u kontejnerima.

1909
01:28:50,579 --> 01:28:53,439
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde da, ajde da...

1910
01:28:53,439 --> 01:28:55,180
[SPEAKER_01] Manavarski prostor je bio mali.

1911
01:28:55,180 --> 01:28:56,520
[SPEAKER_01] Kad sam odlučio da više

1912
01:28:56,520 --> 01:28:57,539
[SPEAKER_01] nema smisla,

1913
01:28:57,539 --> 01:28:58,479
[SPEAKER_01] znači da se stvari,

1914
01:28:58,479 --> 01:28:59,680
[SPEAKER_01] fond se posložio,

1915
01:28:59,680 --> 01:29:00,680
[SPEAKER_01] fond je efikasan,

1916
