[SPEAKER_01] mi smo uklanjali zgrade

1917
01:29:02,159 --> 01:29:03,659
[SPEAKER_01] također po zakonu o građenju.

1918
01:29:03,920 --> 01:29:05,159
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, zanemarivali smo

1919
