1923
01:29:10,579 --> 01:29:11,720
[SPEAKER_01] ali nije bilo jednostavno

1924
01:29:11,720 --> 01:29:12,640
[SPEAKER_01] odluka ministarstva

1925
01:29:12,640 --> 01:29:13,180
[SPEAKER_01] i nije bilo

1926
01:29:13,180 --> 01:29:14,359
[SPEAKER_01] podzakonskog akta

1927
01:29:14,359 --> 01:29:14,979
