1928
01:29:14,979 --> 01:29:16,220
[SPEAKER_01] da naručite takve radove.

1929
01:29:16,220 --> 01:29:18,600
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde da provamo

1930
01:29:18,600 --> 01:29:19,319
[SPEAKER_00] završiti u nekom

1931
01:29:19,319 --> 01:29:20,460
[SPEAKER_00] optimističnijem tonu.

1932
01:29:20,460 --> 01:29:22,199
[SPEAKER_00] Često spominjate sintagmu

1933
01:29:22,199 --> 01:29:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] ekonomski patriotizam.

1934
01:29:23,539 --> 01:29:24,760
[SPEAKER_00] Što bi to trebalo značiti?

1935
01:29:24,760 --> 01:29:26,840
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, ekonomski patriotizam

1936
01:29:26,840 --> 01:29:29,079
[SPEAKER_01] je zapravo

1937
01:29:29,079 --> 01:29:30,300
[SPEAKER_01] vrlo jednostavan koncept.

1938
01:29:30,300 --> 01:29:31,359
[SPEAKER_01] On se sastoji od toga

1939
01:29:31,359 --> 01:29:32,800
[SPEAKER_01] da imate duboko razumijevanje

1940
01:29:32,800 --> 01:29:33,560
[SPEAKER_01] da sistemski

1941
01:29:33,560 --> 01:29:35,239
[SPEAKER_01] kada vi pomažete

1942
01:29:35,239 --> 01:29:36,659
[SPEAKER_01] određenu domaću kompaniju

1943
01:29:36,659 --> 01:29:37,899
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo pomažete sebi.

1944
01:29:37,899 --> 01:29:39,180
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, primjerice,

1945
01:29:39,180 --> 01:29:39,760
[SPEAKER_01] ako ja

1946
01:29:39,760 --> 01:29:42,819
[SPEAKER_01] evo, ja kad radim investicije

1947
01:29:42,819 --> 01:29:44,100
[SPEAKER_01] stvarno se trudim

1948
01:29:44,100 --> 01:29:45,899
[SPEAKER_01] da veliku većinu stvari

1949
01:29:45,899 --> 01:29:47,039
[SPEAKER_01] koje god mogu naručiti

1950
01:29:47,039 --> 01:29:48,079
[SPEAKER_01] naručim da od hrvatskih

1951
01:29:48,079 --> 01:29:49,319
[SPEAKER_01] proizvodjača i dobavljača.

1952
01:29:49,319 --> 01:29:50,460
[SPEAKER_01] Bez obzira što je možda

1953
01:29:50,460 --> 01:29:52,760
[SPEAKER_01] i stranac vlasnih kompanije

1954
01:29:52,760 --> 01:29:54,739
[SPEAKER_01] ako je proizvodnja u Hrvatskoj

1955
01:29:54,739 --> 01:29:55,979
[SPEAKER_01] ona ima kontribuciju

1956
01:29:55,979 --> 01:29:56,699
[SPEAKER_01] IBDP-u

1957
01:29:56,699 --> 01:29:58,680
[SPEAKER_01] ali i porezima koje se plaćaju.

1958
01:29:58,840 --> 01:30:01,420
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, recimo da nama sad dođe neka kompanija

1959
01:30:01,420 --> 01:30:02,579
[SPEAKER_01] evo, indijska recimo

1960
01:30:02,579 --> 01:30:04,779
[SPEAKER_01] i da napravi kompaniju

1961
01:30:04,779 --> 01:30:06,840
[SPEAKER_01] koja će zaposliti 30.000 ljudi.

1962
01:30:06,840 --> 01:30:08,979
[SPEAKER_01] Da li će nama biti bolje?

1963
01:30:08,979 --> 01:30:10,359
[SPEAKER_01] Pa naravno da će nam biti bolje.

1964
01:30:10,359 --> 01:30:12,039
[SPEAKER_01] Da li ću ja rađe kupiti od njih

1965
01:30:12,039 --> 01:30:13,239
[SPEAKER_01] ili od neke druge kompanije?

1966
01:30:13,239 --> 01:30:15,239
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ja ću rađe kupiti od njih.

1967
01:30:15,319 --> 01:30:17,659
[SPEAKER_01] Jer dokle god su oni tu i dokle god funkcioniraju

1968
01:30:17,659 --> 01:30:19,899
