1974
01:30:28,979 --> 01:30:31,779
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, zatvoreni ekonomski sustav

1975
01:30:31,779 --> 01:30:34,420
[SPEAKER_01] je jedan sistem kojem vi doprinosite

1976
01:30:34,420 --> 01:30:35,720
[SPEAKER_01] kad mu pomažete.

1977
01:30:36,060 --> 01:30:37,220
[SPEAKER_01] Ali vi ste dio tog sustava.

1978
01:30:37,220 --> 01:30:38,699
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, vama će biti bolje.

1979
01:30:38,699 --> 01:30:40,979
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, primjerice, dođe ta indijska kompanija

1980
01:30:40,979 --> 01:30:43,739
[SPEAKER_01] i sad naši proračunski prihodi

1981
01:30:43,739 --> 01:30:44,560
[SPEAKER_01] budu puno bolji

1982
01:30:44,560 --> 01:30:45,880
[SPEAKER_01] i dođe premijer i kaže

1983
01:30:45,880 --> 01:30:48,659
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću sniziti PDV za 2%, 3%, 4%.

1984
01:30:48,659 --> 01:30:49,579
[SPEAKER_01] Je li nama bolje?

1985
01:30:49,579 --> 01:30:50,680
[SPEAKER_01] Pa bolje nam je.

1986
01:30:50,680 --> 01:30:52,739
[SPEAKER_01] Prena tome, ekonomski patriotizam

1987
01:30:52,739 --> 01:30:55,020
[SPEAKER_01] osim romantičnog ovog dijela,

1988
01:30:55,020 --> 01:30:56,500
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, patriotizam i općenito

1989
01:30:56,500 --> 01:30:57,800
[SPEAKER_01] svi vuku na romantiku.

1990
01:30:57,800 --> 01:31:01,020
[SPEAKER_01] Patriotizam ima duboku, pragmatičnu misu u sebi.

1991
01:31:01,020 --> 01:31:03,520
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, moje države i svim građanima

1992
01:31:03,520 --> 01:31:04,479
[SPEAKER_01] onutar te države

1993
01:31:04,479 --> 01:31:06,220
[SPEAKER_01] će biti bolje

1994
01:31:06,220 --> 01:31:07,939
[SPEAKER_01] ako nam je svima bolje.

1995
01:31:07,939 --> 01:31:09,939
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ako mi svi vozimo Mercedes,

1996
01:31:09,939 --> 01:31:10,680
[SPEAKER_01] svi ne vozite,

1997
01:31:10,680 --> 01:31:12,539
[SPEAKER_01] kolika je vjerojatnost da ćete ga vi voziti?

1998
01:31:12,539 --> 01:31:13,100
[SPEAKER_01] Ogromno.

1999
01:31:13,100 --> 01:31:15,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ako mi, niko od nas nema auto,

2000
01:31:15,380 --> 01:31:17,439
[SPEAKER_01] kakva je šansa da ćete vi voziti Mercedes?

2001
01:31:17,439 --> 01:31:18,199
[SPEAKER_01] Nikako.

2002
01:31:18,199 --> 01:31:20,079
[SPEAKER_01] Prena tome, kad je svima bolje,

2003
01:31:20,079 --> 01:31:22,180
[SPEAKER_01] velika je vjerojatnost da će i vama biti bolje.

2004
01:31:22,180 --> 01:31:23,939
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ekonomski patriotizam

2005
01:31:23,939 --> 01:31:26,159
[SPEAKER_01] je vezan uz ideju da nam svima bude bolje,

2006
01:31:26,159 --> 01:31:28,020
[SPEAKER_01] a da će onda i meni biti bolje

2007
01:31:28,020 --> 01:31:29,399
[SPEAKER_01] kao pojedinci u tom sistemu.

2008
01:31:29,399 --> 01:31:31,199
[SPEAKER_00] Kužim, hvala vam puno na pošinju.

2009
01:31:31,199 --> 01:31:32,340
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vama i hvala vam na pozornost.

2010
01:31:32,340 --> 01:31:34,340
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, još samo jedna stvar,

2011
01:31:34,340 --> 01:31:36,159
[SPEAKER_00] treba bih vas pitati nešto vezano uz mlade.

2012
01:31:36,159 --> 01:31:39,159
[SPEAKER_00] Koju poruku na kraju imate vezano za mlade?

2013
01:31:39,159 --> 01:31:40,699
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, gdje da se ukriče,

2014
01:31:40,699 --> 01:31:41,380
[SPEAKER_00] šta da rade,

2015
01:31:41,380 --> 01:31:42,260
[SPEAKER_00] kako da napredaju,

2016
01:31:42,260 --> 01:31:43,840
