2017
01:31:43,840 --> 01:31:45,880
[SPEAKER_00] najbolje moguće?

2018
01:31:45,939 --> 01:31:47,760
[SPEAKER_00] Možete uopće tako nešto reći?

2019
01:31:47,760 --> 01:31:51,319
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno, da neko ima odgovor na to pitanje,

2020
01:31:51,319 --> 01:31:52,399
[SPEAKER_01] to bi bilo prekrasno,

2021
01:31:52,399 --> 01:31:54,119
[SPEAKER_01] ali ja sam puno knjige pročitao,

2022
