[SPEAKER_01] ne znam odgovor.

2023
01:31:54,779 --> 01:31:57,560
[SPEAKER_01] Ali se, pokazam se svojim znanjem i iskustvom

2024
01:31:57,560 --> 01:31:58,500
[SPEAKER_01] da impak imate neko...

2025
01:31:58,500 --> 01:31:59,399
[SPEAKER_01] Ono koja vam mogu reći oko toga

2026
01:31:59,399 --> 01:32:00,460
[SPEAKER_01] kaj bi trebali raditi,

2027
01:32:00,460 --> 01:32:01,960
