2028
01:32:01,960 --> 01:32:03,579
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, opet, ja vam 55 godina

2029
01:32:03,579 --> 01:32:05,060
[SPEAKER_01] i dan danas ne znam kaj bi radio.

2030
01:32:05,060 --> 01:32:06,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bih malo studirao,

2031
01:32:06,659 --> 01:32:08,060
[SPEAKER_01] ja bih se malo bavio softwarima,

2032
01:32:08,060 --> 01:32:09,100
[SPEAKER_01] ja bih se malo simital.

2033
01:32:09,520 --> 01:32:11,600
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, opustite se, budite radoznali,

2034
