[SPEAKER_01] radite kaj god.

2035
01:32:12,460 --> 01:32:13,840
[SPEAKER_01] Život je dovoljno dugačak

2036
01:32:13,840 --> 01:32:15,739
[SPEAKER_01] da možete imati dvije, tri karijere.

2037
01:32:15,739 --> 01:32:18,140
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što mislim da je jako važno

2038
01:32:18,140 --> 01:32:20,079
[SPEAKER_01] da mladi razumiju još jednom,

2039
01:32:20,079 --> 01:32:21,319
[SPEAKER_01] a rekao sam na početku,

2040
01:32:21,319 --> 01:32:24,340
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, vi mladi ste bolja verzija naš starih.

2041
01:32:24,340 --> 01:32:26,899
[SPEAKER_01] Nemojte nas zamjeriti kad mi vas gledamo,

2042
01:32:26,899 --> 01:32:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] gledamo vas kroz spektar naših iskustava

2043
01:32:29,000 --> 01:32:29,859
[SPEAKER_01] i uvijek smo zabrinuti,

2044
01:32:29,859 --> 01:32:31,359
[SPEAKER_01] joj ti mladi, kak bu to završilo.

2045
01:32:31,359 --> 01:32:32,800
[SPEAKER_01] Bolje bu završilo,

2046
01:32:32,800 --> 01:32:34,140
[SPEAKER_01] ali vi ste bolja verzija nas.

2047
01:32:34,380 --> 01:32:36,180
[SPEAKER_01] Na tome, nemojte se s tim opće optarečivati.

2048
01:32:36,180 --> 01:32:37,739
[SPEAKER_01] I nemojte se suzdržavati.

2049
01:32:37,739 --> 01:32:40,899
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što naš obrazovni sustav ukupno radi je

2050
01:32:40,899 --> 01:32:42,699
[SPEAKER_01] da vas tjera da ste suzdržani,

2051
01:32:42,699 --> 01:32:44,439
[SPEAKER_01] da smo svi mediokriteti i tak dalje.

2052
01:32:44,439 --> 01:32:46,899
[SPEAKER_01] Hrvati su, kao human capital,

2053
01:32:46,899 --> 01:32:49,060
[SPEAKER_01] pogledajte recimo i taj Microsoft-ov indeks

2054
01:32:49,060 --> 01:32:50,039
[SPEAKER_01] za digitalizaciju,

2055
01:32:50,039 --> 01:32:51,760
[SPEAKER_01] su iznad prosjeka Evrope.

2056
01:32:51,760 --> 01:32:54,699
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerujte mi, Hrvati su i u sportu zato takvi

2057
01:32:54,699 --> 01:32:56,199
[SPEAKER_01] i tu je najlakše to pokazati,

2058
01:32:56,199 --> 01:32:57,819
[SPEAKER_01] jer u sportu su pravila jasno.

2059
01:32:57,819 --> 01:33:00,300
[SPEAKER_01] U Hrvatskoj Narodnoj Banci

2060
01:33:00,300 --> 01:33:01,560
[SPEAKER_01] sve drugačije zapošljava,

2061
01:33:01,819 --> 01:33:03,680
[SPEAKER_01] ali u sportu ne mene tako zapošljavati.

2062
01:33:03,680 --> 01:33:04,140
[SPEAKER_01] Ili tako?

2063
01:33:04,140 --> 01:33:06,800
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da budite, imajte povjerenje u sebe,

2064
01:33:06,800 --> 01:33:08,899
[SPEAKER_01] radite stvari koje mislite da treba.

2065
01:33:08,899 --> 01:33:10,020
[SPEAKER_01] Najvažnije u životu je,

2066
01:33:10,020 --> 01:33:11,159
[SPEAKER_01] zamislite sad ste mladi,

2067
01:33:11,159 --> 01:33:13,460
[SPEAKER_01] sad vas zanima ovo, ono, ljevo, desno,

2068
01:33:13,460 --> 01:33:14,720
[SPEAKER_01] curaj, dečki i ne znam kaj,

2069
01:33:14,720 --> 01:33:16,180
[SPEAKER_01] ali kad budete stariji,

2070
01:33:16,180 --> 01:33:18,680
[SPEAKER_01] nećete ni moći jesti kaj hoćete,

2071
01:33:18,680 --> 01:33:20,279
[SPEAKER_01] nećete imati neke boleste,

2072
01:33:20,279 --> 01:33:24,380
[SPEAKER_01] nećete možda ni seks moći aplicirati koliko želite

2073
01:33:24,380 --> 01:33:26,279
[SPEAKER_01] i ostaćete sami sa sobom.

2074
01:33:26,279 --> 01:33:28,560
[SPEAKER_01] I vaša savjest i to što ste vi radili u životu

2075
01:33:28,560 --> 01:33:29,479
[SPEAKER_01] je najjača.

2076
01:33:31,819 --> 01:33:35,460
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da ćete jedino imat sami sebe i svoju savjest.

2077
01:33:35,460 --> 01:33:37,960
[SPEAKER_01] Napravite stvari kak mislite da treba,

2078
01:33:37,960 --> 01:33:38,859
[SPEAKER_01] nemojte se bojati.

2079
01:33:38,859 --> 01:33:41,220
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek će vam neko pružiti ruku kad padnete

2080
01:33:41,220 --> 01:33:43,020
[SPEAKER_01] i meni se to događalo u životu.

2081
01:33:43,020 --> 01:33:45,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi koji nikad nisam očekio su mi pružili ruku kad sam pao,

2082
01:33:45,699 --> 01:33:48,680
[SPEAKER_01] jer su vjerovali da ono što ja radim je dobro.

2083
01:33:48,680 --> 01:33:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] To će se dovoljiti vama.

2084
01:33:50,000 --> 01:33:51,899
[SPEAKER_01] Budite hrabri, radite ono što treba.

2085
01:33:51,899 --> 01:33:53,340
[SPEAKER_01] Imate povjerenje o sebe.

2086
01:33:53,819 --> 01:33:56,640
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste vi iskoristili svoju mladost kako ste željeli?

2087
01:33:56,640 --> 01:33:58,079
[SPEAKER_00] Kako biste trebali?

2088
01:33:58,079 --> 01:34:00,119
[SPEAKER_01] Nikon vam nikad ne iskoristi sve kako bi htio.

2089
01:34:00,119 --> 01:34:04,819
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, kad kupite neki auto samljako ili kupite motor pa kažete ja ću se voziti svaki dan.

2090
01:34:04,819 --> 01:34:06,479
[SPEAKER_01] Ma nećete se voziti svaki dan.

2091
01:34:06,479 --> 01:34:10,720
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, lako je iz perspektive, kad neko vrijeme prođe,

2092
01:34:10,720 --> 01:34:12,699
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek je lako gledati retrogradno i reći,

2093
01:34:12,760 --> 01:34:14,779
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam mogao ovo, ja sam mogao ovo.

2094
01:34:14,779 --> 01:34:17,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mislim da sam imao jednu lijepu mladost tu na Pešćenici u Zagrebu.

2095
01:34:17,739 --> 01:34:21,359
[SPEAKER_01] Igrali smo nogomet na cesti jer nije bilo puno auti i tak dalje.

2096
01:34:21,359 --> 01:34:23,619
[SPEAKER_01] Igrali smo lovice, lopove, žandra, ovo.

2097
01:34:23,619 --> 01:34:24,800
[SPEAKER_01] Imali smo lijepo djetnjstvo.

2098
01:34:24,800 --> 01:34:28,180
[SPEAKER_01] Školovanje je bilo pravedno.

2099
01:34:28,180 --> 01:34:31,600
[SPEAKER_01] Ono kaj svoje djeci sad kažem kad se žale na neke profesore.

2100
01:34:31,600 --> 01:34:35,619
[SPEAKER_01] Školovanje vam je najpravedniji dio vašeg života.

2101
01:34:35,619 --> 01:34:37,899
[SPEAKER_01] Kad uđete u biznis ili, ne da bože, u politiku,

2102
01:34:37,899 --> 01:34:39,539
[SPEAKER_01] tu ima puno nepravde.

2103
01:34:39,539 --> 01:34:41,399
[SPEAKER_01] Tu ima puno pokvarenosti.

2104
01:34:41,600 --> 01:34:42,779
[SPEAKER_01] Školovanje je još uvijek bez obzira

2105
01:34:42,779 --> 01:34:44,460
[SPEAKER_01] kad ponekad neki profesor ipak ima

2106
01:34:44,460 --> 01:34:46,619
[SPEAKER_01] od 1 do 5 su grube ocjene.

2107
01:34:46,619 --> 01:34:48,520
[SPEAKER_01] Da li si 4 ili 5 ili 2 ili 3.

2108
01:34:48,520 --> 01:34:50,920
[SPEAKER_01] To zgleda puno, ali zapravo u ukupnosti

2109
01:34:50,920 --> 01:34:53,119
[SPEAKER_01] školovanje je jedan pravedan sustav.

2110
01:34:53,119 --> 01:34:55,140
[SPEAKER_01] Školujte se, naučite se

2111
01:34:55,140 --> 01:34:57,539
[SPEAKER_01] da jedino teškim radom možete nesto postići.

2112
01:34:57,539 --> 01:34:59,340
[SPEAKER_01] Odvučite se šta želite postići.

2113
01:34:59,340 --> 01:35:01,140
[SPEAKER_01] Ako želite osvojiti novac,

2114
01:35:01,140 --> 01:35:02,300
[SPEAKER_01] to je kredibilan cilj,

2115
01:35:02,300 --> 01:35:03,460
[SPEAKER_01] zaradite novac.

2116
01:35:03,460 --> 01:35:05,939
[SPEAKER_01] Ali vjerujte da je to znanje puta energija.

2117
01:35:05,939 --> 01:35:08,060
[SPEAKER_01] Sve ovo, ja ću ovako, ja ću, ne znam,

2118
01:35:08,060 --> 01:35:09,880
[SPEAKER_01] kriptovaluta, joj moj najmluči si vam keže

2119
01:35:09,880 --> 01:35:11,619
[SPEAKER_01] tata ću se obogatiti na kriptovaluta.

2120
01:35:11,619 --> 01:35:13,920
[SPEAKER_01] Moje rekao sreće, možda da, a možda i ne.

2121
01:35:13,920 --> 01:35:16,100
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, neizvjesnost je velika

2122
01:35:16,100 --> 01:35:17,239
[SPEAKER_01] i to je rizični kapital.

2123
01:35:17,239 --> 01:35:19,819
[SPEAKER_01] Uloži malo novaca i igre se da nešto naučiš.

2124
01:35:19,819 --> 01:35:22,079
[SPEAKER_01] Sve je to fora, ali rekao...

2125
01:35:22,079 --> 01:35:23,560
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je dobar uvod u novi podcast.

2126
01:35:23,560 --> 01:35:25,720
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala vam puno Damjera što ste došli.

2127
01:35:25,720 --> 01:35:28,060
[SPEAKER_00] Želijem puno uspjeha u svim danednim projektima.

2128
01:35:28,060 --> 01:35:29,439
[SPEAKER_01] I alamu.

